Loewe Eyes New Markets With Shareholder Sharp, FTD Says

-- B y   A l l i s o n   C o n n o l l y
-- 
2011-08-29T06:11:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-29/loewe-eyes-new-markets-with-shareholder-sharp-ftd-says.html
German television maker  Loewe AG (LOE) 
aims to expand into new markets with support from Sharp Corp.,
its majority shareholder, the Financial Times Deutschland
reported today, citing an interview with Chief Executive Officer
Oliver Seidl.  Loewe is talking to Sharp about intensifying their
cooperation, Seidl said in the interview. Loewe could develop
software and technology for Sharp for the European market, and
they could buy components together, the newspaper cited him as
saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Allison Connolly in  Frankfurt  at 
 aconnolly4@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at   pserafino@bloomberg.net . 